title Transportation Logistics Landscape — Goods from Producers to the Public

// ===== Anchors (users) =====
component The Public [0.96, 0.60]
component Consumers [0.94, 0.58]
component Producers [0.93, 0.30]
component Society [0.92, 0.35]
component Government [0.91, 0.25]

