// =========================================================
// Dependencies (a -> b means a depends on b; nu(a) >= nu(b))
// =========================================================

// Users to the core outcomes
The Public -> Goods Delivered to the Public
Consumers -> Goods Delivered to the Public
Consumers -> Shops
Consumers -> E-commerce
Producers -> Long Haul Transport
Producers -> Logistics Hubs
Society -> Awareness of Supply Chain
Society -> Territorial / CNI Sovereignty
Government -> Logistics Regulation
Government -> Territorial / CNI Sovereignty

