Goods Delivered to the Public -> Shops
Goods Delivered to the Public -> E-commerce
Goods Delivered to the Public -> Last Mile Delivery
Goods Delivered to the Public -> Real-time Stock Visibility

// Awareness and regulation touch the whole chain
Awareness of Supply Chain -> Logistics Data
