E-commerce -> Real-time Stock Visibility
Real-time Stock Visibility -> Logistics Data
Real-time Stock Visibility -> Telematics

// Fulfilment dependencies
Last Mile Delivery -> Delivery Operations
Last Mile Delivery -> Automated Delivery (robots/lockers)
