// =========================================================
// Movement (evolve) — components expected to drift rightward
// =========================================================

// Automated delivery pressure — scenario-specified acceleration
evolve Autotrucks (autonomous HGV) 0.55 label [-10, 5]
evolve Delivery Drones 0.50 label [-5, 10]
evolve Automated Delivery (robots/lockers) 0.60 label [-10, 5]
evolve Scouts (route/advance vehicles) 0.55 label [-5, 5]

// Electrification of powertrain
evolve Electric Powertrain 0.82 label [-5, 5]

// Awareness and sovereignty rising up the agenda
evolve Awareness of Supply Chain 0.45 label [-10, 5]
evolve Territorial / CNI Sovereignty 0.40 label [-10, 5]

// Real-time stock visibility and telematics heading toward commodity
evolve Real-time Stock Visibility 0.75 label [-5, 5]
evolve Telematics 0.85 label [-5, 5]

// Regulation evolving to catch up with automation
evolve Logistics Regulation 0.70 label [-10, 5]

// =========================================================
// Inertia (advisory — OWM has no first-class inertia keyword;
// annotated here and in output.md)
// =========================================================
// - Fossil-fuel Powertrain: sunk capex in diesel fleets; tank/pump infra.
// - HGV Driver Skills: unionised, licensed; workforce reshaping is slow.
// - Shops: physical retail footprint and leases resist channel shift.
// - Fuel Supply: entrenched distribution and tax regimes.
